  "detailed_description": "Kings and Goblins is a old-school difficult 2D platformer. <br><br>The Goblin Lord has led a horde of goblins to conquer the King's castle.<br>You will play as the King who has lost everything, fight through 3 levels to reach the Goblin Lord and finally get revenge. Free the castle, the Throne awaits you.<br><br>Unlock 2 additional game modes as soon as you beat the game:<br><br><u>Hardcore mode</u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No level selection, you have to beat the game all at once.<br></li><li> All Hearts pickups disappear.<br></li><li> You start the game with only 1 Heart.</li></ul><br><u>Speedrun mode</u><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> No level selection, you have to beat the game all at once.<br></li><li> A stopwatch will appear counting your game time (How fast can you beat the game??)<br></li><li> Your time will be saved and shown on the ranking page if you hit the top 5.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore all levels to collect all diamonds.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852650/extras/b327497b73a2f63e4bd61a5e54cc9231.poster.avif?t=1712936811\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852650/extras/b327497b73a2f63e4bd61a5e54cc9231.webm?t=1712936811\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852650/extras/b327497b73a2f63e4bd61a5e54cc9231.mp4?t=1712936811\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Avoid the goblins' traps.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2852650/extras/c1399d58dba82bce33601749e7c065a7.poster.avif?t=1712936811\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a